title: BigFish Games - 7 Wonders - Treasures of Seven, match 3 [h33t][w
description:
Ancient builders constructed their mist important structures on mystic 

sites. Together, the sites reveal the hidden CITY OF GODS and the 

Treasure of Seven.

You are invited to participate in the creation of these greatest 

achievements. Three compasses activated along the journey point to the 

hidden city. Only THE most skilled and determined voyagers will reveal 

the secrets of the ages.

thanx to TAC-CM
